title: 'Disable the httpd_verify_dns SELinux Boolean'

description: |-
    By default, the SELinux boolean <tt>httpd_verify_dns</tt> is disabled.
    If this setting is enabled, it should be disabled.
    <sebool-macro enable="false" sebool="httpd_verify_dns" />

